Package: buffy
Title: An R Package With Advanced Buffering for Geometry Objects
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Chandler", "Armstrong", email = "omni.armstrong@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides functions for generating advanced types of buffers around
  geometry objects.  Generates buffers on the WSG84 ellipsoid or in Euclidean
  geometry, as appropriate.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
Imports: dplyr,
  geosphere,
  rgeos,
  sf,
  sp,
  units
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
